This week on Taking Stock we take a look at the re-opening of schools during the COVID-19 pandemic. Bruce Whitfield is joined by Stacey Brewer Co-Founder SPARKS School, Shaun Green Chairman of association of homeschoolers and Professor Mary Metcalfe Education Expert to unpack whether schools are ready to re-open during this pandemic and other precautionary measures parents can take to educate their kids from home.